  }, "v3"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c c\u1EADu c\u1EE7a A-bi-m\xEA-l\xE9c n\xF3i chuy\u1EC7n v\u1EDBi c\xE1c l\xE3nh t\u1EE5 S\xEA-chem v\u1EC1 \xFD ki\u1EBFn n\u1EA7y. H\u1ECD li\u1EC1n quy\u1EBFt \u0111\u1ECBnh \u0111i theo A-bi-m\xEA-l\xE9c v\xEC h\u1ECD n\xF3i, \"Anh ta th\xE2n thu\u1ED9c v\u1EDBi ch\xFAng ta.\" "), mdx("h6", {
